This application categorises the TV shows based on their genere and is sorted based on the ratings of the show. It is also provided with the search field to get the shows based on you preference
### The framework and libraries used in this project are:
    Node : v22.14.0
    npm : v10.9.2
    Framework: Vue.js 3 - v3.5.24,
    Routing : vue-router - v4.6.4
    HTTP Client: Axios - v1.13.2,
    State Management : Pinia - v3.0.4,
    Styling : Tailwind CSS - v3.4.19
    Build Tool : Vite

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v16 or above)
- npm

### Installation: 
    npm install 

### To run the project:
    npm run dev

### Features:
    1. User can browse for the shows based on the genre of the shows and further they are sorted based on their ratings in the dashboard.
    2. User can search for the particular show by entering the show name.
    3. When clicked on the particular show , user will be navigated to another page which holds the show details.Search is keyboard accessible.
